WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.773 --> 00:00:02.133
Good evening, family.

00:00:02.133 --> 00:00:03.291
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.291 --> 00:00:05.083
Thank you for joining me again tonight.

00:00:05.083 --> 00:00:11.880
We have a lot of work to do, things I have in my spirit to pray about.

00:00:11.880 --> 00:00:15.618
We aren't going to waste a lot of time because I came on late.

00:00:16.631 --> 00:00:21.387
It takes me a little bit because I haven't been eating fast food junk.

00:00:21.680 --> 00:00:24.799
I cook my food fresh every day using whole foods.

00:00:27.039 --> 00:00:29.040
I am trying to do well and keep my calories logged.

00:00:29.440 --> 00:00:37.648
Diana found a neat app that helps me weigh my food in a bowl every day to track how many ounces I'm eating.

00:00:37.648 --> 00:00:39.120
It's a real treat.

00:00:40.491 --> 00:00:46.800
I'm not complaining, Father; I'm so thankful I am able to measure and weigh our food.

00:00:49.631 --> 00:00:50.015
Not that you probably care, but it's interesting.

00:00:53.386 --> 00:01:02.590
That is why it takes me a little longer; I am navigating a new learning curve.

00:01:02.590 --> 00:01:10.130
We are going to pray real quick, and then I'll let you go so you can have your night.

00:01:10.130 --> 00:01:19.239
Most of you are probably going to bed, but I felt in my heart when Braden was telling me the news about reports of Iranians hiding missiles.

00:01:19.239 --> 00:01:22.994
If you go back three videos, the Spirit of God showed us massive underground tunnels.

00:01:26.815 --> 00:01:28.455
I said you could use a train to move through them based on what I was seeing.

00:01:29.622 --> 00:01:37.013
There were railroad cars for these heavy missiles.

00:01:37.467 --> 00:01:46.799
I saw them moving them on flatbed carts, similar to the rails used in mining to lift coal or gold.

00:01:46.799 --> 00:01:52.720
They were long and filled with missiles and various military equipment underground.

00:01:52.720 --> 00:02:01.973
Reports today suggest they know about 50%, though it changes constantly due to fake news and AI videos.

00:02:01.973 --> 00:02:13.340
From what I understand, they have quite a few found silos or missile hiding spaces, but they still cannot find 50% or more of them.

00:02:13.340 --> 00:02:24.126
They're using our big bombers with payloads of 70,000 lbs to drop on these targets to try to reach underground and bust these so-called tunnels.

00:02:24.126 --> 00:02:28.110
Braden found an announcement this morning.

00:02:46.697 --> 00:02:47.051
This is Iran bragging that they have all this underground, saying, 'We're fixing to use all this on you.

00:02:47.051 --> 00:02:49.990
' Braden posted things on X for you.

00:02:49.990 --> 00:02:56.060
I want to see the one with the tunnels.

00:02:56.060 --> 00:03:04.900
I didn't get to watch it all the way through.

00:03:22.160 --> 00:03:25.760
Braden said this goes along with what the Lord showed me.

00:03:25.760 --> 00:03:27.333
Look at those tunnels.

00:03:27.333 --> 00:03:35.470
I don't see railroad tracks, so I don't know about that.

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:40.640
This looks like they have wheels and can be moved that way.

00:03:40.640 --> 00:03:47.840
In what I saw, it looked sandy, and they were taking them from one bunker to another to avoid detection.

00:03:47.840 --> 00:03:49.456
These are massive underground facilities.

00:03:49.456 --> 00:03:51.866
Do you know how much money that is?

00:03:51.866 --> 00:03:54.347
My goodness, that's a lot of money to build those tunnels underground.

00:03:54.347 --> 00:03:57.528
Look at all that weaponry.

00:03:57.528 --> 00:04:03.059
As I was shown in the spirit, they were all connected like ant dens.

00:04:05.050 --> 00:04:16.000
You can stir the top of the ant den, but you're only seeing the effect on top, not what is going on underneath.

00:04:18.670 --> 00:04:18.940
They have all this underground.

00:04:24.080 --> 00:04:24.460
I saw bunkers deep down.

00:04:24.460 --> 00:04:33.623
The more they were being attacked by America, the deeper they would put their equipment to avoid being annihilated.

00:04:33.623 --> 00:04:37.780
Braden said this matches what the Lord showed me.

00:04:37.780 --> 00:04:44.520
There are reports about other things the United States has hit.

00:04:44.520 --> 00:04:49.129
They're saying they have a missile coming out of a tunnel.

00:04:51.200 --> 00:04:51.440
That massive thing looked like a megaton.

00:05:01.555 --> 00:05:01.893
I guess we hit it, but look how big that thing is.

00:05:14.204 --> 00:05:14.400
That's what I feel in my heart.

00:05:14.400 --> 00:05:15.680
Excuse my allergies; I'm overcoming them tonight.

00:05:15.680 --> 00:05:19.839
Spring has sprung before officially getting here in Oklahoma.

00:05:20.439 --> 00:05:25.909
The trees and flowers are blooming, and I pray we don't have a freeze that kills them.

00:05:26.594 --> 00:05:32.399
I thought it was interesting that Emmanuel Macron jumped in the fight tonight.

00:05:32.399 --> 00:05:35.500
Did anybody hear what Emmanuel Macron said?

00:05:35.500 --> 00:05:37.840
Go ahead and play Emmanuel Macron.

00:05:37.840 --> 00:05:45.911
Basically, Emmanuel Macron is saying he is taking his boat and will start beefing up his nuclear capabilities.

00:05:45.911 --> 00:05:49.720
It goes along with what I have seen concerning Emmanuel Macron.

00:05:51.719 --> 00:05:59.063
The Lord said in the days ahead he will be raised up to be a tyrant.

00:05:59.063 --> 00:06:00.840
Is he doing that now?

00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:04.617
No, he's just acting like he wants to be involved.

00:06:18.160 --> 00:06:18.448
I believe what the Lord showed us last video was when I saw Turkey building and taking over that Strait area, that little crossing.

00:06:25.700 --> 00:06:29.199
I was shown by the Spirit of God Turkey rising up, and I saw massive war drums beating in the Black Sea.

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:43.600
I saw the Turkish leader, whether he is the prime minister or president—I don't know his title—put on a Count Dracula cape with a massive collar and a brooch.

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:46.679
He looked like he was from an old Dracula movie with slicked-back hair.

00:06:46.679 --> 00:06:52.000
Braden made an AI image of it.

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:59.259
He looked toward the west at the waterway to the Ukraine area and southern Europe.

00:06:59.259 --> 00:07:02.599
He was eyeing it.

00:07:02.599 --> 00:07:07.199
Then I heard him having a meeting with Vladimir Putin.

00:07:07.199 --> 00:07:14.000
They were discussing how they were done playing the cat and mouse game.

00:07:29.520 --> 00:07:29.840
I heard unconventional weapons of war, like we've never seen before, being used by Putin.

00:07:29.840 --> 00:07:30.960
Mega stuff.

00:07:40.099 --> 00:07:40.279
I saw Turkey being involved to block the waterway to get into the Black Sea to defend and try to help with Ukraine and the things ahead.

00:07:46.434 --> 00:07:55.618
I saw Russia annihilating Zelensky and doing the thing, and I saw above Ukraine and in this area WW3 really big across it, and I saw it go from all over Europe.

00:07:55.618 --> 00:07:56.791
That's what I saw right there.

00:08:08.799 --> 00:08:09.119
The Dardanelles straits?

00:08:09.119 --> 00:08:13.310
Yeah, can you show them?

00:08:13.310 --> 00:08:25.656
That's what I saw, Turkey taking over and making it where it was impossible to go into the Black Sea.

00:08:25.656 --> 00:08:29.607
Now, I don't know if there's any other ways.

00:08:29.607 --> 00:08:32.1000
But what I saw—where's Ukraine at?

00:08:32.1000 --> 00:08:35.599
Ukraine's right there.

00:08:35.599 --> 00:08:37.839
It's like you see Constantinople.

00:08:37.839 --> 00:08:43.310
No, you got to move it down.

00:08:43.310 --> 00:08:45.600
Okay, that's where Ukraine's at.

00:08:45.600 --> 00:08:47.480
I see it here.

00:08:47.480 --> 00:08:54.347
So that's why I saw them controlling that to try to help Russia.

00:08:54.347 --> 00:09:06.297
Then I saw Kim Jong-un sending tens of thousands of troops to Ukraine and helping Iran in the days ahead, flexing.

00:09:06.297 --> 00:09:16.755
He started to become paranoid because he thinks he's next, which I pray with all my heart he is.

00:09:16.755 --> 00:09:23.800
Wouldn't that be wonderful if he was removed, too?

00:09:23.800 --> 00:09:29.160
That man is terrible to those North Koreans.

00:09:29.160 --> 00:09:29.920
He's crazy, too.

00:09:29.920 --> 00:09:48.120
As I was seeing, I linked it back to what the Lord showed me concerning the Olympics and that satanic thing in that arch when I told you.

00:09:48.120 --> 00:10:11.290
People said, 'Brandon, that's not a word,' but they were conjuring up the Hitler spirit by satanic practice, bringing forth through these tablets that I saw—old ancient satanic writing that was like in hieroglyphics on tablets.

00:10:12.930 --> 00:10:35.248
I don't know what this was, but it was on a black, like onyx-looking tablet, and they were trying to read through AI scans because it's hard for them to understand what it was.

00:10:48.640 --> 00:10:50.460
But they were trying to scan it with an AI, with a computer, with quantum computing to try to open up portals to bring forth the antichrist, the Mahdi.

00:10:50.460 --> 00:10:56.383
What is even being said all over the world right now?

00:10:56.383 --> 00:11:07.876
Even Diana said this morning somebody sent her an article from, I believe it was a major news channel, saying that's what these major religious people are saying.

00:11:07.876 --> 00:11:19.509
We have been—Iran has been prepared for this for decades now, waiting for this event.

00:11:19.509 --> 00:11:21.291
That's Fox.

00:11:21.291 --> 00:11:26.529
Okay, so you found it.

00:11:26.529 --> 00:11:31.279
They can see it.

00:11:31.279 --> 00:11:33.559
It's Fox.

00:11:50.520 --> 00:11:50.880
So they are all ready and preparing for who they call the Mahdi.

00:12:04.663 --> 00:12:05.269
And they said that this major event had to happen, and they're excited about it.

00:12:09.538 --> 00:12:13.257
And they've been prepared and have been preparing for decades now because they want the Mahdi to come.

00:12:32.959 --> 00:12:33.137
And they know he'll come through war.

00:12:33.137 --> 00:12:48.940
Whenever Diana was reading—she read the whole thing to me—I said, 'Oh my gosh, do we really realize that even the Islamic world realizes how close we are to the end of the end?

00:12:48.940 --> 00:12:51.165
' And they're preparing for it.

00:12:51.165 --> 00:13:05.493
They needed this war with Israel and with America, the great Satan, to stir it all up, to bring forth their Islamic savior.

00:13:05.493 --> 00:13:08.080
And this is during Ramadan.

00:13:20.800 --> 00:13:21.320
This is all during their Ramadan.

00:13:39.449 --> 00:13:39.839
And the Lord said, 'This is why I'm praying over America and our soil.

00:13:39.839 --> 00:13:44.880
' And the Lord said, 'Pray over Easter.

00:13:44.880 --> 00:13:58.720
' If you remember, a week or two weeks ago, the Lord said—I don't even remember now how far—he said, 'Pray over Easter.

00:13:58.720 --> 00:14:06.844
' It's just a week later, after Ramadan is over, that Easter and Palm Sunday take place.

00:14:06.844 --> 00:14:18.093
So we're praying over our churches for America and for surprise attacks, for our Homeland Security to find all of it, for the FBI, all of it.

00:14:18.093 --> 00:14:23.839
There's a lot of chatter, from what I understand.

00:14:23.839 --> 00:14:30.126
So with all that being said, folks, this is just escalating.

00:14:40.773 --> 00:14:41.120
You know, I talked to Pastor Candace where we go to church.

00:14:41.120 --> 00:15:08.249
She called last night, going over everything of what I believe the Lord has been showing me and relating it to Bible prophecy and where we are with the signs of the times of the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ and the revival that we believe we're right there.

00:15:26.399 --> 00:15:32.720
She told Diana and me, 'I've been reading books on the glory, stirring myself up on old books of the glorious church rising and old prayer books about the glory and meditating on the glory and walking in it like an Azusa Street and stirring myself up.

00:15:32.720 --> 00:15:56.570
' If I go back to what the Lord said even about the false alien visitations that I believe we'll have in the days ahead with the wars and the rumors of wars and everything he said about Matthew 24 and the men being offended and the great apostasies and the falling away and all the things.

00:15:56.570 --> 00:16:04.240
Then we got John Bevere's book today, 'The King is Coming,' I believe is what it's called.

00:16:04.240 --> 00:16:20.857
I'm going to tell you the first chapter—I'm going to be real with you and always tell you the truth—the first chapter was kind of boring.

00:16:20.857 --> 00:16:24.160
It's just the opening, get you ready for it.

00:16:24.160 --> 00:16:26.559
Second chapter better.

00:16:26.559 --> 00:16:34.929
By the time Diana got into the fourth, fifth, and sixth chapters, she read to me in the car.

00:16:42.171 --> 00:16:46.399
It seemed like all evening she's been reading to me because she loves John Bevere's books and she's like, 'Oh my god, this book is phenomenal.

00:16:46.399 --> 00:16:50.449
' But when I first heard the first chapter, I thought it was kind of slow.

00:17:05.130 --> 00:17:05.416
And then all of a sudden you felt the anointing shift and I thought, 'Woohoo!

00:17:05.416 --> 00:17:06.559
It's a winner.

00:17:06.559 --> 00:17:12.229
' And so I got so excited, especially the chapter about the Jewish wedding ceremony.

00:17:19.885 --> 00:17:20.148
Phenomenal.

00:17:20.674 --> 00:17:22.091
I didn't know the custom.

00:17:22.091 --> 00:17:34.640
If we go back to the vision that I had where Jesus was standing underneath the hoopa—it was the pillar, the post, and there were olive leaves carved into it, and it was all in this lacquer.

00:17:52.787 --> 00:17:53.360
It was beautiful.

00:17:53.360 --> 00:18:00.928
This hoopa with lace and all kinds of things on it, and he was waiting on the bride.

00:18:00.928 --> 00:18:04.889
He was a flame of fire there waiting.

00:18:15.726 --> 00:18:20.820
And as he goes into the Jewish wedding ceremony and how it correlates—it's a type and shadow of Jesus coming back for his church—it was the most beautiful thing to me personally.

00:18:20.820 --> 00:18:26.360
I told Diana, 'I could read that chapter four or five times.

00:18:26.360 --> 00:18:43.840
' Because of our culture, we're ignorant Americans; we don't know much about Jewish culture and what it meant for Jesus and what he was talking about.

00:18:43.840 --> 00:18:53.069
But even when John Bevere said the disciples did—well, yeah, because that was their tradition, that's the way they lived.

00:19:06.583 --> 00:19:11.074
But us, we don't know the tradition of Jewish culture back when Jesus's timeframe was.

00:19:13.280 --> 00:19:22.062
But he describes it all and how it correlates with the body of Christ right now, and I was like, 'Oh my gosh, this is so cool.

00:19:22.062 --> 00:19:26.023
' And so it blessed me a lot.

00:19:28.240 --> 00:19:40.480
Like I said, I haven't read the whole book, so I can't tell you I love the whole thing, but I can tell you from what I have heard my wife read to me, it is an A+ so far.

00:19:40.480 --> 00:19:42.550
I give it an A+.

00:19:55.573 --> 00:20:03.542
He goes into pre-trib, mid-trib, and post-trib, right?

00:20:03.542 --> 00:20:03.919
Yeah.

00:20:03.919 --> 00:20:13.480
So you hear his point of view about it and how he brings scripture into it and where his stance is, which is just like mine.

00:20:13.480 --> 00:20:15.360
We're not appointed unto wrath.

00:20:15.360 --> 00:20:19.700
I believe with all my heart that God's not a wife-beater.

00:20:19.700 --> 00:20:30.933
And it goes along even with the point of what I've told you of keeping your lamps full of oil, not being in bed with the world.

00:20:30.933 --> 00:20:33.840
Be separate unto him.

00:20:33.840 --> 00:20:40.826
Be expecting a purified bride, a purified Jewish culture.

00:20:41.953 --> 00:20:44.680
A bride was waiting for her husband for that year.

00:20:44.950 --> 00:20:53.890
He even said that the bride was not in bed with the world; she was separated for her groom.

00:20:54.533 --> 00:20:57.200
It was just the stuff that was the type and shadow.

00:20:57.839 --> 00:20:58.479
My goodness.

00:20:58.799 --> 00:21:03.066
This is why I've been telling you: you must get on fire for Jesus.

00:21:03.066 --> 00:21:05.600
You must be all-in.

00:21:05.600 --> 00:21:09.360
You have to get your lamp full of oil.

00:21:09.360 --> 00:21:12.559
It's time to get out of compromise.

00:21:12.559 --> 00:21:18.080
You have to be that bride, that vessel without spot or wrinkle.

00:21:18.320 --> 00:21:22.293
The only way you're going to do that is by being separate and holy unto him.

00:21:23.858 --> 00:21:26.987
Like Billy Burke, we talk about God.

00:21:26.987 --> 00:21:29.902
I have all of God; God needs more of me while he's inside of me.

00:21:32.196 --> 00:21:40.320
He is dwelling on the inside of me, but I've got to die to self and give him more of me.

00:21:40.320 --> 00:21:43.886
It's the refining fire; it's coming up higher.

00:21:43.886 --> 00:21:49.492
You can either fly with the crows or you can fly with an eagle.

00:21:49.919 --> 00:21:55.760
The Lord showed me about the prophetic yesterday.

00:21:55.760 --> 00:21:58.540
He said, "You want to know more about the prophetic?

00:21:58.540 --> 00:22:02.106
" I said, "Yeah, I would like to know.

00:22:02.106 --> 00:22:11.280
When I get to a certain place in the visions that you're showing me, it feels like a lid.

00:22:12.013 --> 00:22:15.679
" He said, "It's on purpose.

00:22:16.728 --> 00:22:29.120
The higher you go with me, the greater the responsibility for what I reveal to you, so you can't just flippantly say everything out of your mouth.

00:22:30.120 --> 00:22:35.611
" There were three different levels of the prophetic that he showed me.

00:22:36.960 --> 00:22:44.903
He said this level down here, you can see as a watchman; you're able to see with your natural eye what I want to say.

00:22:44.903 --> 00:22:49.080
I'm just paraphrasing, so just follow me.

00:22:50.849 --> 00:22:59.813
You're on the wall and you can see, but then at the next level, you have magnifying glasses and you can see magnified; you can see quite a ways.

00:22:59.813 --> 00:23:10.400
But then when you get to the next level, you've got radar, and the radar is going beep-beep, and you're going, "Oh, I didn't see that.

00:23:10.400 --> 00:23:11.133
" Why?

00:23:11.133 --> 00:23:14.799
Because it's Holy Ghost radar.

00:23:15.724 --> 00:23:29.147
As I was seeing in the spirit, the higher you go with him, the more you are required to keep your mouth shut until he is releasing you to say more.

00:23:31.300 --> 00:23:36.880
To whom much is given, much is required.

00:23:37.160 --> 00:23:45.474
Down here, he said that's where a lot of people dwell because that's where their trust level is.

00:23:46.537 --> 00:23:50.880
To go from glory to glory requires trust.

00:23:50.880 --> 00:23:56.950
To whom much is given, much is required.

00:23:56.960 --> 00:24:12.549
Do you want to walk in the greater manifestations of me like Elijah, like the prophets of old who were more sold out?

00:24:12.559 --> 00:24:23.977
There is a level of intimacy that a lot of the culture today has no idea about.

00:24:24.286 --> 00:24:34.799
That's what he was talking to me about over the last 48 hours since the last video we did.

00:24:35.797 --> 00:24:41.707
I know the price because it costs a lot.

00:24:41.707 --> 00:24:46.720
Just to get where I am right now has cost a lot.

00:24:47.084 --> 00:24:59.626
I said, "Lord, to get to the next summit, to go higher and fly in the higher space with the eagles, to go from glory to glory...

00:24:59.626 --> 00:25:02.319
" the air gets even thinner the higher you go.

00:25:13.120 --> 00:25:19.360
It's all about dying to self and not worrying about what people think.

00:25:19.360 --> 00:25:31.190
So, all that being said, it's a cultivation.

00:25:31.680 --> 00:25:33.600
Where are we today?

00:25:33.600 --> 00:25:38.720
I try to keep you updated on what's going on in my own personal life and what he talks to me about.

00:25:41.634 --> 00:25:53.919
He starts talking about investments, how to grow your money, and being blessed, going from glory to glory, being a steward over what he's given you, and how he cares about every little thing in your life.

00:25:54.669 --> 00:25:58.982
He cares about your finances, your health, eating right, and taking care of your temple.

00:26:00.400 --> 00:26:05.028
He wants us to go from glory to glory and live a long life.

00:26:07.626 --> 00:26:13.840
He wants us, beloved—I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers.

00:26:16.760 --> 00:26:31.029
And if you're not prospering in your soul, you aren't prospering in the natural.

00:26:31.279 --> 00:26:38.799
I want to be blessed in the city and in the field, coming in and going out, but not only that, in my soul—your mind, will, and emotions.

00:26:38.979 --> 00:26:41.528
You do that by renewing your mind with the Word of God.

00:26:41.786 --> 00:26:43.733
It's not just a one-time thing.

00:26:44.320 --> 00:26:59.860
I think it was FF Bosworth who said people eat three times a day for their flesh and only one little bit of food for their spirit once a week on Sundays.

00:26:59.860 --> 00:27:05.520
They feed their flesh all week long but only feed their spirit one meal a week.

00:27:06.320 --> 00:27:10.435
I was thinking about that, and it's the truth for many.

00:27:11.110 --> 00:27:28.862
I truly believe the reason the Lord brought me on YouTube, X, and all these other platforms is to tell people that he's coming, but also that you must have a relationship with him and be intimate with him through the Word of God, prayer, and separation.

00:27:34.240 --> 00:27:37.120
You have to come up higher.

00:27:37.544 --> 00:27:46.080
I told you very strongly—I even told my little brother—that you don't understand, a storm's coming.

00:27:46.080 --> 00:27:52.720
I heard one lightning strike, and we never heard any more lightning or thunder that night.

00:27:53.742 --> 00:27:56.240
It was just that one moment.

00:27:58.000 --> 00:28:09.470
I said, "A storm is coming," and then it went crack—it was loud and shook the house.

00:28:09.470 --> 00:28:14.599
Never again did it the rest of the time; it didn't even rain.

00:28:15.039 --> 00:28:19.668
Most people said that was AI or that we made it up.

00:28:20.660 --> 00:28:25.799
I'm telling you on a stack of Bibles, it was real.

00:28:27.700 --> 00:28:30.640
We did not make that up with AI.

00:28:30.640 --> 00:28:36.080
That was the Lord, and it was a sign.

00:28:37.550 --> 00:28:38.860
I'm not here to try to deceive you.

00:28:45.120 --> 00:28:48.480
It was the Lord trying to warn you.

00:28:49.040 --> 00:28:55.120
As it shook the house, it tripped me out.

00:28:55.120 --> 00:28:56.320
I had goosebumps on goosebumps.

00:28:59.619 --> 00:29:00.177
Braden and I were just looking at each other.

00:29:01.466 --> 00:29:13.120
After it was over, that's all we could talk about because of the force of the thunder; it shook the whole home.

00:29:13.463 --> 00:29:20.693
I thought, "Oh my goodness, Lord, you're a God of signs," but it's an emphasis.

00:29:20.693 --> 00:29:23.721
He's emphasizing where we are.

00:29:23.721 --> 00:29:26.549
There's a storm coming.

00:29:29.600 --> 00:29:36.960
Yesterday the Lord said Xi Jinping has made his decision.

00:29:41.039 --> 00:29:53.190
He's getting ready to implement the plan concerning Taiwan.

00:29:53.476 --> 00:30:01.469
I do not want to say this to scare you; I say this to prepare you to pray.

00:30:01.919 --> 00:30:07.440
As I was seeing that, it took three days to overthrow it.

00:30:07.440 --> 00:30:09.689
I saw it happen again.

00:30:09.689 --> 00:30:18.799
It took three days, similar to what happened with Maduro.

00:30:25.679 --> 00:30:36.070
They came in like stealth in the middle of the night, and there was not much of a fight.

00:30:36.080 --> 00:30:37.093
I saw it.

00:30:37.093 --> 00:30:38.782
Now, can we change it?

00:30:38.782 --> 00:30:40.170
I believe we can.

00:30:40.170 --> 00:30:44.897
I believe there are things we can pray and stop or delay.

00:30:44.897 --> 00:30:46.924
But this is what I see.

00:30:46.924 --> 00:30:47.902
I see in part.

00:30:49.716 --> 00:31:03.280
I saw into Russia, the cat and mouse, and these unconventional weapons of war—weapons we've never seen before out of Russia.

00:31:03.280 --> 00:31:12.500
They aren't holding back the big stuff anymore, using weapons that were shock and awe.

00:31:12.500 --> 00:31:17.600
Then I want to show you the clip concerning the gas wars.

00:31:18.480 --> 00:31:25.749
Braden made this short and said, "Daddy, do you remember saying this?

00:31:25.749 --> 00:31:29.447
" I said, "Yeah, I remember part of it.

00:31:31.896 --> 00:31:39.840
" This was on June 1st, 2025.

00:31:39.840 --> 00:31:41.333
So, here we are.

00:31:41.707 --> 00:31:44.160
I gave this word from the Lord.

00:31:44.160 --> 00:31:46.330
Now, are we about to see that?

00:31:47.080 --> 00:31:54.230
I don't try to add to or take away from anything and say, 'Well, that's where we are right now.

00:31:54.240 --> 00:32:00.452
' But if I go by what I saw, could we be there?

00:32:00.746 --> 00:32:03.600
In my opinion, we could.

00:32:03.600 --> 00:32:07.039
We could be right there.

00:32:07.233 --> 00:32:13.778
I thought this was interesting because Braden found this; he was looking through my videos to find things for shorts.

00:32:15.449 --> 00:32:22.900
Look at what the Lord said: 'I saw a great war breaking out with Israel and Iran in the days ahead.

00:32:22.900 --> 00:32:31.897
' I told you back in January that I saw an American missile striking a mountain that was an underground city.

00:32:32.366 --> 00:32:37.006
Iran set all kinds of deterrents trying to stop this missile.

00:32:37.006 --> 00:32:38.720
It was a very powerful one.

00:32:38.720 --> 00:32:46.914
When Israel does this, I saw that they set Iran back financially, nuclear—everything.

00:32:57.440 --> 00:32:58.080
I heard the Spirit of the Lord say they put them back in the Stone Age.

00:32:58.080 --> 00:33:06.240
When they do this, they strike their refineries, and I saw gas and oil prices skyrocketing.

00:33:06.240 --> 00:33:11.120
I've warned you about this since 2023.

00:33:11.120 --> 00:33:17.831
Then the Lord showed me in that vision the 1970s gas wars.

00:33:31.253 --> 00:33:31.458
I saw cars lined up down the blocks because of gas shortages.

00:33:44.690 --> 00:33:44.880
It would bring the price of oil up to $200 a barrel.

00:33:52.500 --> 00:33:54.200
Big money trying to flow would stimulate the American economy whenever these big oil productions get hit in the Middle East.

00:33:54.200 --> 00:34:01.530
It would happen for a season, for a window.

00:34:06.880 --> 00:34:07.280
I don't know how long, but for a window.

00:34:11.966 --> 00:34:12.503
I saw 'drill, baby, drill.

00:34:12.503 --> 00:34:19.019
' I saw pipelines being opened up and worked out, making major agreements.

00:34:19.019 --> 00:34:22.427
The Nord Stream pipeline, I believe, is what it's called.

00:34:26.511 --> 00:34:35.860
I saw it being talked about and opened up, trying to get this deal going, doing major oil deals ahead and stimulating America's economy.

00:34:35.860 --> 00:34:46.399
But when this happens, I saw great antisemitism because people are mad at Israel about what they're about to do.

00:34:46.399 --> 00:34:51.480
Remember this: I saw them wanting to retaliate with war—Russia, Syria, Turkey.

00:34:53.867 --> 00:34:55.644
I saw them getting upset in the Middle East against Israel.

00:34:55.644 --> 00:34:57.609
Have we changed it through prayer?

00:35:14.167 --> 00:35:14.495
I don't believe we have.

00:35:20.240 --> 00:35:20.490
So, are we there?

00:35:21.240 --> 00:35:21.490
I don't know.

00:35:32.419 --> 00:35:32.829
It looks like something, doesn't it?

00:35:32.829 --> 00:35:36.027
Can we stop it through prayer?

00:35:41.968 --> 00:35:44.096
A lot of the visions that the Lord gives me, we change through prayer.

00:35:51.036 --> 00:35:53.113
I don't consider myself a prophet; I've said that a thousand times.

00:36:02.365 --> 00:36:02.891
I believe I'm a watchman.

00:36:09.599 --> 00:36:38.160
The Lord said, 'I've called you to go on YouTube and pray and I will show you things that are going to happen in the future about world events and you will change it through prayer on this channel—governmental things, voting, all of it.

00:36:38.160 --> 00:36:42.760
' That's my main focus.

00:36:50.600 --> 00:36:50.880
A lot of people ask, 'Is that prophetic?

00:36:50.880 --> 00:36:56.410
' I see things and the Lord tells me to pray.

00:36:56.410 --> 00:36:58.420
So, is that prophetic?

00:36:58.420 --> 00:37:02.530
You label me whatever you want; I don't care.

00:37:08.720 --> 00:37:09.080
I don't label myself.

00:37:14.240 --> 00:37:14.448
I just keep close to Him.

00:37:14.448 --> 00:37:18.919
But whenever I see part of a word coming to pass, I start to look.

00:37:21.440 --> 00:37:24.160
It was a window; it doesn't last very long.

00:37:24.160 --> 00:37:41.119
As I told you, Venezuela and Iran and all these were trying to be part of the BRICS in the days ahead.

00:37:41.119 --> 00:37:46.440
I saw Trump strategically—Braden has the videos—eliminating the new BRICS system so that it becomes weak.

00:37:46.440 --> 00:37:47.560
They needed funding.

00:37:47.560 --> 00:37:53.857
Venezuela, Iran's oil, and other nations in Africa rising up to back the BRICS currency.

00:38:09.707 --> 00:38:10.009
I saw Trump attacking that.

00:38:10.009 --> 00:38:12.719
This is exactly what I believe is happening.

00:38:31.789 --> 00:38:32.043
It makes the dollar strong and makes it where they don't have a BRICS anymore.

00:38:32.043 --> 00:38:33.061
BRICS goes away.

00:38:34.523 --> 00:38:40.169
As I saw Macron and these other men, they try to rise up a greater war in Europe to support the euro.

00:38:41.936 --> 00:38:43.760
I saw the euro would be in trouble and war break out.

00:38:59.040 --> 00:38:59.760
It all goes to a digital platform in the days ahead to a beast system with crypto, and the foundation is being laid.

00:39:05.253 --> 00:39:05.480
I don't know, folks.

00:39:05.480 --> 00:39:17.039
All I know is when I see all the signs of the times all around us right now, it sure looks like the Book of Revelation.

00:39:21.938 --> 00:39:22.169
It looks like the things that we've been waiting for.

00:39:22.169 --> 00:39:23.822
It's time to get serious with Jesus.

00:39:23.822 --> 00:39:28.493
It's time to get your heart right, get out of compromise, and put your eyes to the skies.

00:39:28.493 --> 00:39:32.196
People ask, 'Brandon, where do you think it could come?

00:39:32.196 --> 00:39:35.920
' I look for Him every day.

00:39:35.920 --> 00:39:45.884
But I know I usually look around the Jewish feast time frames—Rosh Hashanah—during that time frame for what Sister Billie and everybody teaches.

00:39:45.884 --> 00:39:47.920
I'm not an eschatology expert, y'all.

00:39:47.920 --> 00:39:52.640
It's hard for me to understand the Book of Revelation, but I try.

00:40:03.599 --> 00:40:03.909
I study as much as I can with Perry Stone and other men like Rick Renner.

00:40:11.403 --> 00:40:11.599
I try to grasp what they say, but they're over my head a lot of times.

00:40:11.599 --> 00:40:18.000
John Bevere's book was the easiest for me to understand so far.

00:40:18.000 --> 00:40:20.000
He doesn't try to talk in algebra.

00:40:24.470 --> 00:40:24.980
I can grasp that.

00:40:24.980 --> 00:40:26.384
Make it simple.

00:40:26.384 --> 00:40:29.467
If my kid, Paisley, can't understand it, then it's too complicated.

00:40:29.467 --> 00:40:31.120
Make it where people can grab a hold of it.

00:40:31.120 --> 00:40:39.387
If you try to talk about living by faith in a way that people can't get a hold of it, how are you going to go from glory to glory?

00:40:39.387 --> 00:40:44.700
Faith comes by hearing and hearing by the word of God.

00:40:44.700 --> 00:40:54.043
If you don't understand the preacher because he talks too educated, then you've got to simplify it for some folks.

00:40:54.043 --> 00:41:05.119
I'm not trying to be belittling; I'm just saying if you don't have a PhD in theology, make it where someone who is a mechanic can understand.

00:41:05.119 --> 00:41:08.420
Who cares?

00:41:21.360 --> 00:41:21.840
The mechanic fixing your car is probably making more money anyway if he has his own body shop.

00:41:21.840 --> 00:41:35.840
It's just interesting to me because so many people try to be so educated when they talk and you walk away not understanding a thing.

00:41:55.100 --> 00:41:55.320
I try to make it simple based on what I know, as someone who barely passed high school with a GED.

00:41:55.760 --> 00:41:59.246
I keep pushing and grab a hold of what God has given me.

00:41:59.246 --> 00:42:07.600
I'm a bulldog on a bone; I'm not giving up until I've got a hold of it.

00:42:10.000 --> 00:42:16.916
I liked what I heard about John Bevere's book today from what my wife read me.

00:42:18.942 --> 00:42:21.413
I hope that blessed you.

00:42:22.738 --> 00:42:30.100
I tried not to make it too long, but I ended up talking too much.

00:42:30.100 --> 00:42:38.120
Then I saw this man be assassinated on a stage with microphones in front of him.

00:42:38.120 --> 00:42:54.440
He was behind a pulpit talking to a crowd, and it looked like he was appointed to be the leader over that nation.

00:42:54.440 --> 00:43:04.027
As he was talking, someone from the right took him out.

00:43:11.795 --> 00:43:13.619
It went through his collarbone area—he probably had a bulletproof vest on—but it went through his neck area and out.

00:43:29.466 --> 00:43:29.933
He was done.

00:43:29.933 --> 00:43:35.720
As I watched this, I heard the people screaming.

00:43:50.941 --> 00:43:51.270
I could see it in the vision.

00:43:54.560 --> 00:44:03.320
I heard the people screaming and acting up, freaking out because of what they just witnessed.

00:44:03.720 --> 00:44:06.331
But they brought in another after this man was taken over.

00:44:06.331 --> 00:44:17.520
I saw this man after he was done; I saw a bad leader come in again, and the Lord—I heard Him say, "I told you the window of this.

00:44:17.520 --> 00:44:27.610
" I mean, I told you this would be a window, not a door—not like Cuba, not like Mexico, not like Venezuela.

00:44:27.610 --> 00:44:39.420
I'll bring in leaders for those nations, and great revival will come forth out of there, but there'll be a longer time frame.

00:44:39.420 --> 00:44:45.760
I saw Iran flip quickly back to bringing in some bozo like the Ayatollah again.

00:44:45.760 --> 00:44:51.227
It was a window for the church to have a major revival.

00:45:03.390 --> 00:45:03.740
So I pray for that man, Reza Pahlavi, or whatever his name is.

00:45:06.800 --> 00:45:07.040
I pray for his safety.

00:45:08.149 --> 00:45:11.776
I don't wish evil upon anybody; I tell you what I see.

00:45:11.776 --> 00:45:15.191
It was a very colorful vision, very bold.

00:45:15.191 --> 00:45:21.710
I could see the microphones that were in front of his face.

00:45:38.820 --> 00:45:39.030
I don't know where he was.

00:45:45.840 --> 00:45:46.133
It looked to be like sandstone buildings around him.

00:46:07.440 --> 00:46:07.760
They were like a yellow-looking color, almost like a burnt red-orange looking color building—some kind of sandstone or stucco.

00:46:07.760 --> 00:46:11.737
But as I saw that, it was short-lived.

00:46:11.737 --> 00:46:30.399
You can let a bird out of a cage, but if they know how to live in bondage and they've never been free before, they don't know how to fly.

00:46:30.399 --> 00:46:36.630
They don't know how to get out and be done.

00:46:36.630 --> 00:46:38.319
They're so used to living in bondage.

00:46:38.319 --> 00:46:50.411
People have been so used to living in bondage for decade after decade since the 1970s.

00:46:50.411 --> 00:46:56.551
They said when the Ayatollah got in there, and then here we are.

00:46:56.969 --> 00:47:01.119
You can free them, but are they free inside?

00:47:01.119 --> 00:47:11.429
It’s the same thing with Egypt, the same thing with the children of Israel coming out of Egypt.

00:47:11.429 --> 00:47:32.100
They were bound inside their minds, and it took a whole new generation to come up and let the old ones die off before they could go and take the land.

00:47:32.100 --> 00:47:42.053
You've got to get stinking thinking out of your thinking and realize that you're more than a conqueror—that God has come to set you free.

00:47:42.053 --> 00:47:45.787
But as long as you think bound, you'll be bound.

00:47:45.787 --> 00:47:49.240
As a man thinketh in his heart, so is he.

00:47:51.724 --> 00:47:52.658
And that's what the Lord is showing me.

00:48:02.439 --> 00:48:02.739
I can free them, Brandon.

00:48:02.739 --> 00:48:06.571
I can free them, but they're not free.

00:48:06.571 --> 00:48:20.994
Even if I let them out and open the cage door and say, "Free bird, fly," they're so used to being on that perch, being the one trapped, that they don't realize the door's open and they have an opportunity.

00:48:20.994 --> 00:48:27.879
They still think back and go back to the way they were in bondage.

00:48:27.879 --> 00:48:29.620
It was better in Egypt.

00:48:29.620 --> 00:48:31.720
It was better in Egypt.

00:48:31.720 --> 00:48:36.000
Even after I freed them: "It's better in Egypt.

00:48:36.640 --> 00:48:41.520
" I give them manna from heaven—and John said in that book, it was boxcars full of manna.

00:48:41.520 --> 00:49:01.706
Every morning God provided a miracle—huge amounts of food, thousands and thousands of pounds for millions of people.

00:49:01.706 --> 00:49:11.349
Every morning God provided, but it's better in Egypt because Egypt was still inside of them.

00:49:11.359 --> 00:49:14.240
They didn't realize, "We're free.

00:49:14.240 --> 00:49:20.352
We can take the land.

00:49:20.352 --> 00:49:26.897
The God of Abraham, Isaac, and Jacob is with us.

00:49:26.897 --> 00:49:31.520
" They didn't want to go up on the mountain; they sent Moses.

00:49:32.827 --> 00:49:38.960
I refuse to allow the devil to keep me bound in my thinking.

00:49:54.120 --> 00:49:54.415
It's time to come up higher and realize who we are.

00:49:54.415 --> 00:49:58.792
He's the accuser of the brethren, folks.

00:49:58.792 --> 00:50:04.292
He tries to tell you all the time you're a loser, but we're winners.

00:50:04.292 --> 00:50:06.690
Jesus made us winners; we're more than conquerors.

00:50:06.690 --> 00:50:12.293
So, Father, we just thank You for the body that was broken for us.

00:50:25.420 --> 00:50:28.880
As we praise You tonight for all that You've done for setting us free, Father, thank You, Lord, for the Iranian people, that they'll take hold of this opportunity and get ready for the greatest revival they've ever seen.

00:50:28.880 --> 00:50:34.277
It will be all around them if they'll grab hold of it—the church.

00:50:34.277 --> 00:50:40.427
They'll take this opportunity and bring in the souls all throughout the region.

00:50:48.400 --> 00:50:48.800
I thank You, Father, for the body that was broken.

00:50:48.800 --> 00:50:55.520
You were wounded for our transgressions; You were bruised for our iniquities.

00:50:57.884 --> 00:51:01.120
The chastisement of our peace was upon You, and with Your stripes, we are healed.

00:51:01.120 --> 00:51:09.636
We thank You, Lord, that we don't have to be sick in our bodies anymore.

00:51:09.636 --> 00:51:17.964
We thank You, Lord, that we walk in divine health, and we take this body in the name of Jesus and receive it by faith.

00:51:17.964 --> 00:51:19.298
We have a covenant.

00:51:19.298 --> 00:51:21.806
This is a cup of the covenant.

00:51:21.806 --> 00:51:26.280
Jesus took it all, and we don't have to have it.

00:51:26.280 --> 00:51:29.180
Father, I thank You, Lord, that our sins are forgiven.

00:51:33.350 --> 00:51:46.613
The moment we confess our sins, You are faithful and just to forgive us and cleanse us of all unrighteousness.

00:51:46.613 --> 00:51:54.319
We plead the blood, we apply the blood, and we make much of the blood.

00:52:05.973 --> 00:52:06.267
The blood makes much of us.

00:52:06.267 --> 00:52:07.860
We thank You, Lord.

00:52:07.860 --> 00:52:16.827
There's a bloodline around us: over my mind, over my health, over my finances, over my wife, my children, all of us—God, my dogs.

00:52:16.827 --> 00:52:18.500
Father, I thank You, Lord.

00:52:30.240 --> 00:52:30.579
The blessing of the Lord is on our house.

00:52:35.240 --> 00:52:40.520
Father, this is the beginning of March, and I thank You, Lord, that the blood moon was last night.

00:52:54.126 --> 00:52:54.331
The signs of the times are all around us again.

00:52:54.331 --> 00:52:56.319
You're screaming in the sky, Lord.

00:52:56.319 --> 00:52:59.109
You're yelling, telling everybody, "Are we listening?

00:52:59.109 --> 00:53:01.080
Are we listening to what You're saying?

00:53:09.599 --> 00:53:09.839
" I take this blood right now in the name of Jesus, and we apply it to us.

00:53:09.839 --> 00:53:11.809
Amen and amen.

00:53:18.860 --> 00:53:19.090
I have to say one more thing.

00:53:19.550 --> 00:53:28.960
I noticed about two or three weeks ago, when I hear Him and that cloak comes on, I feel like I can hear Him like I'm talking to Braden.

00:53:28.960 --> 00:53:31.359
It's that loud.

00:53:31.359 --> 00:53:46.560
But I noticed as I had gotten an offense in my heart—and we were reading "The Bait of Satan" and getting that offense out—it sounded like He was talking like this.

00:54:06.649 --> 00:54:07.040
I told Diana, "It's not deep; it's shallow.

00:54:07.040 --> 00:54:10.708
" It's not like it's coming on all the way.

00:54:15.520 --> 00:54:16.080
I don't understand what's going on.

00:54:16.080 --> 00:54:25.240
But that's why I take time and I don't make videos; I get quiet.

00:54:25.240 --> 00:54:27.412
When I don't hear Him, I freeze.

00:54:27.412 --> 00:54:31.279
If you aren't hearing Him real clear, I check my thermostat.

00:54:31.439 --> 00:54:41.359
I know because He's always there and He's always talking to me, but when He talks and it doesn't sound very clear, like He's muffled, He's still saying the same thing.

00:54:41.359 --> 00:54:48.747
But as soon as that happens, I check my heart because it's the flesh that's in the way.

00:54:48.747 --> 00:55:04.347
So if you feel like God's trying to tell you something and you can't understand what He's saying, check your heart, check your flesh, check your thermostat.

00:55:25.120 --> 00:55:25.680
You're in the way.

00:55:26.960 --> 00:55:28.693
So I started saying, "Well, Lord, something's wrong.

00:55:33.519 --> 00:55:34.719
" I took that time, and then Diana got sick with COVID and all that.

00:55:39.050 --> 00:55:43.733
I got real quiet, and He said, "Examine yourself.

00:55:43.733 --> 00:55:52.079
All it takes is to go just a little bit off course to go way off course over time.

00:55:52.079 --> 00:56:02.230
" And that's what I was trying to tell you all as I was examining the offense in my heart.

00:56:02.240 --> 00:56:30.592
The moment I started praying for those that despitefully used me and came against me—people I felt offended by—I started praying for them and lifting them up, and it became loud again.

00:56:43.520 --> 00:56:44.009
How do you love your brother?

00:56:44.009 --> 00:56:48.307
Check your love walk, your love thermostat.

00:56:48.307 --> 00:56:52.159
Love takes no account of a suffered wrong.

00:56:52.159 --> 00:56:53.920
What does that mean?

00:56:58.760 --> 00:57:00.200
I don't care who's talking trash about you; I'm walking in love.

00:57:00.200 --> 00:57:02.560
Check your love thermostat.

00:57:26.360 --> 00:57:29.280
I don't care what the email says or what you get in the mail from some sister that writes you a long letter telling you off.

00:57:30.537 --> 00:57:32.799
I don't care what you say, sister.

00:57:32.799 --> 00:57:39.812
I'm following what the voice of the Lord told me to do, and I forgive you.

00:57:39.812 --> 00:57:43.279
But it's easy to take offense.

00:57:43.279 --> 00:57:53.690
That's why I'm saying when you get that root of offense and you keep stacking them up in there, eventually he starts talking like this.

00:57:53.690 --> 00:57:59.120
But he's saying the same thing, and he's still there.

00:57:59.120 --> 00:58:01.324
What's wrong with you, Brandon?

00:58:01.324 --> 00:58:03.030
It's not my Father.

00:58:03.030 --> 00:58:05.420
Why are you talking like this, Lord?

00:58:05.420 --> 00:58:09.883
Why is it not so deep, Lord?

00:58:09.883 --> 00:58:17.635
Why doesn't it feel like that cloak coming on like it used to?

00:58:17.635 --> 00:58:21.480
What happened?

